{"title":"来自农村的诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":1,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自农村的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尹一之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在地头上迎接太阳出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在回村的小路上送它下山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳是勤俭的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们却比它来得早归得晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳是守时的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们每天都在那个时候见面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分红场上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李哲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分红的人们匆忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单干户隔墙张望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看社里丰收羡慕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看自己歉收感伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单干户牵马到场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怨过去眼睛不亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当众人要求入社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水滴呀滴进大洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（齐齐哈尔）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修水塘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村前村后找不到人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户锁上了门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆婆当了娃娃司令；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑看孙孙仿造塘埂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两担塘泥一担挑起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年小伙快步如飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘底心多么喜欢呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“可别压坏了你的身体！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}